---
import AboutHeroImage from '../assets/blog-placeholder-about.jpg';
import Layout from '../layouts/BlogPost.astro';
---

<Layout
	title="About LastRite"
	excerpt="Learn about LastRite's mission to honor and celebrate lives"
	category="About"
	author="LastRite Team"
	date={new Date('2026-04-21')}
	readTime="3 min"
	image={AboutHeroImage}
	imageAlt="LastRite team workspace"
	featured={false}
>
	<h2>Our Mission</h2>
	<p>
		LastRite is dedicated to creating a meaningful, dignified platform for families to honor their loved ones.
		We believe that every life deserves to be celebrated, remembered, and shared with care.
	</p>

	<h2>What We Do</h2>
	<p>
		LastRite makes it easy to:
	</p>
	<ul>
		<li><strong>Create obituaries</strong> — Craft beautiful, personalized tributes that capture a life well-lived</li>
		<li><strong>Share memories</strong> — Invite family and friends to contribute their favorite moments and stories</li>
		<li><strong>Organize memorial fundraising</strong> — Support causes that mattered to your loved one</li>
		<li><strong>Preserve legacies</strong> — Keep cherished memories accessible for generations to come</li>
	</ul>

	<h2>Why LastRite</h2>
	<p>
		Obituaries are more than announcements—they're celebrations of life, connection, and legacy. LastRite provides
		families with a compassionate, user-friendly platform to honor those memories in one meaningful place.
	</p>
	<p>
		From the moment someone passes, families need support. LastRite brings together the tools to grieve, celebrate,
		and remember without the added complexity of managing multiple platforms.
	</p>

	<h2>Get Started</h2>
	<p>
		LastRite is currently in development. We'll be launching soon. Check back here or the
		<a href="/starter-blog">memorial stories</a> to stay updated on our progress.
	</p>
</Layout>
